title: Openstreetmap Geofabrik, Bulgaria Roadways, Bulgaria, 2008
name: Openstreetmap Geofabrik, Bulgaria Roadways, Bulgaria, 2008
description: This data set was provided by open street maps and shows various roadways, roads, highways, and paths throughout Bulgaria. seems like a pretty detailed map. Data was uploaded as a polyline shape file. includes attributes for name, type of road, and a one way flag. if value in one way is 0, the road is open for 2 way traffic, if there is a value of 1, there is only 1 way traffic.
